
0.0.5 - 2009-11-21

Added test function with C linkage that can be used by autoconf to check for
library existence.

Added regenauto.sh to regerate libtool/automake/autoconf files.

Fixed simple log format to include cstring for memset function - gcc header
streamlining broke this.

Fixed Makefile.am to include required files in dist target.


0.0.4 - 2007-06-11

XXX - Added Categories to logger, automatically cleaned up on exit

XXX - Ensured logs are flushed on each write

0.0.3 - 2007-01-16

Added initial multithreading support.


0.0.2 - 2007-01-13

Added this log.

Fixed memory leak in time formatting code.

Modified logger to return null streams if the logging level indicates the
message is not to be logged.

Moved examples into their own directory, and added a few more.


0.0.1 - 2007-01-10

Added log format class.

Added simple XML format class.

Added simple printf-like format class.

Improved doxygen docs.


0.0.0-alpha - 2006-05-22

Initial release.
